#: ../../source/vendor/deciso/opncentral.rst:12
msgid ""
"After acquiring a license, you can switch to the commercial software "
"repository containing OPNcentral. In order to install, just go to "
":menuselection:`System->Firmware->Plugins` and search for :code:`os-"
"OPNcentral`."
msgstr ""

