#: ../../source/vendor/deciso/opncentral.rst:84
msgid ""
"When an update is available, it will be shown in the list, including if "
"this upgrade requires a reboot. The upgrade button starts the upgrade "
"procedure, but will only upgrade machines that will require a reboot if "
"**Enable reboot** is checked."
